{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place water into mixing bowl and insert simmering basket, weigh in rice and farro and rinse <nobr>10 sec\/speed 5<\/nobr>. Stir with aid of spatula through hole in mixing bowl lid to ensure a thorough rinsing.","Cook <nobr>32 min\/212°F\/speed 4<\/nobr>. Remove simmering basket with spatula, transfer rice and farro to a bowl and allow to cool. Discard steaming water and dry mixing bowl.","Place flaxseeds, oats and Parmesan into mixing bowl and grate <nobr>10 sec\/speed 10<\/nobr>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside.","Place red bell peppers, onions, carrot, garlic, basil, tomato paste, salt, and chili flakes into mixing bowl and chop <nobr>5 sec\/speed 5<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula and mix a further <nobr>5 sec\/speed 5<\/nobr>.","Add reserved grains and oat-Parmesan mixture and mix <nobr>10 sec\/\/speed 4<\/nobr>.","Divide and shape mixture into four equal-sized patties. Cover loosely with cling wrap and chill for 20 minutes. Heat frying pan over medium high heat and add oil. Fry patties 4 minutes each side or until golden brown.","Serve burgers immediately with your favorite condiment and sliced avocado between toasted buns."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["32 oz water","2 oz brown rice","2 oz farro","2 tbsp flaxseeds","1 oz old fashioned rolled oats","1 oz Parmesan cheese, cut into pieces","2 oz red bell peppers, cut into 1 in. pieces","2 oz yellow onions, cut into 1 in. pieces","1 oz carrots, cut into 1 in. pieces","1 garlic clove","1 tbsp dried basil","2 tbsp tomato paste","½ tsp salt","¼ tsp chili flakes","sunflower oil, to fry","4 hamburger buns, toasted","condiment","avocado, thinly sliced"]}],"id":"r174917","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-2GsDby774Jw\/XZVPlrs3EnI\/AAAAAAAAc6c\/IENDK86PFsQNqxMcvZYo0gxiNUXiI8lbQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_9xJvRaD14tvLty4B.png","title":"Vegetarian Burger","publishedAt":"2017-06-02T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"8 g","fat":"10 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"60 g","calories":"1561 kJ \/ 373 kcal"},"usefulItems":"frying pan, cling wrap, refrigerator","basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 15m","4 portions"]}